<div class="post">
<h2></h2>

<div class="entry">

<ul>
<li>
since October 2013: PhD student at Laboratoire de Physique Statistique. Supervisor: <a href="http://www.lps.ens.fr/~krauth/">Werner Krauth</a>.
</li>
<li>
2011-2013: Master in Theoretical Physics, Utrecht University (the Netherlands).
Research project: Numerical study of trapped and extended Bose-Hubbard models (<a href="http://testweb.science.uu.nl/ITF/teaching/2013/T.Comparin.pdf">pdf</a>).
Supervisor: <a href="http://www.staff.science.uu.nl/~morai101">Cristiane de Morais Smith</a>. 
</li>
<li>
2013, March-June: Research training fellowship for undergraduate students,
International School for Advanced Studies (Trieste, Italy). Topic: Quantum Monte Carlo techniques.
Supervisor: <a href="http://people.sissa.it/~becca">Federico Becca</a>.
</li>
<li>
2007-2011: Bachelor in Physics, Universit&agrave; degli Studi di Milano (Italy).
Research project about the formation of microphases in some soft matter systems (<a href="https://github.com/tcompa/tcompa.github.io-files/blob/master/comparin2011.pdf?raw=true">pdf ita</a>).
Supervisor: <a href="http://www.mi.infm.it/~dpini">Davide Enrico Pini</a>.
</li>
</ul>

<h3>Conferences and schools</h3>
<ul>
<li>
2014, June: <a href="http://comp-phys-2014.sciencesconf.org">4th Les Houches School in computational physics: From quantum gases to strongly correlated systems</a> (Les Houches, France).
</li>
<li>
2012, July: <a href="http://www.democritos.it/school2012/index.php/Main/HomePage" >Summer School on Atomistic Simulation Techniques</a>,
International School for Advanced Studies (Trieste, Italy).
</li>
<li>
2011, August: <a href="http://www.utrechtsummerschool.nl/?type=courses&amp;code=H2">Utrecht Summer School in Theoretical Physics</a> (Utrecht, The Netherlands).
</li>
</ul>

<h3>Other</h3>
<ul>
<li>
2014, January-April: member of the staff for the on-line course <a href="https://www.coursera.org/course/smac">Statistical Mechanics: Algorithms and Computations</a>.
</li>
<li>
12-2010 - 2-2011: Internship at <a href="http://lcm.mi.infn.it/">Computation and Multimedia Laboratory</a>, Physics Department, University of Milan (Italy). Collaboration in a student group for the management of a cluster of about 40 computers, addressed to 200 users. Main activities: hardware maintenance, user assistance and (partial) system administration.
</li>
</ul>

